name: Hanes Men's Hoodie, EcoSmart Fleece Hoodie, Hooded Sweatshirt for Men
small_description: FLEECE TO FEEL GOOD ABOUT – EcoSmart mid-weight cotton/poly fleece with up to 5% of the poly fibers. - CLASSIC SILHOUETTE – Basic hoodie shaping for that sporty look you love. - MADE TO STAY SOFT – Pill-resistant durable fleece stays warm and cozy. - HOLDS ITS SHAPE - Thanks to ribbed cuffs and hem. - MADE TO LAST - Double-needle stitching at the neck and armhole seams for quality and durability, plus a dyed-to-match drawstring at the hood. - CONVENIENT TEARAWAY TAGS - Getting rid of itchy tags is super easy. Simply tear it off for comfort that lasts all day.
full_description: When you're shopping for your next fleece hooded sweatshirt, why not choose one that you can feel good about buying while feeling good wearing? Hanes EcoSmart fleece is your new go-to wardrobe staple. Soft and plush, this cozy hoodie is made of mid-weight cotton/poly fleece with up to 5% of the poly fibers. The fleece in this classic hoodie is pill-resistant, super-soft, and made to keep its plush feel for a long time. And it will hold its shape thanks to ribbed cuffs and hem. Double-needle stitching at the neck and armhole seams further enhance quality and durability. In classic hoodie style, there's also a front kangaroo pocket. Here's a soft, warm, fleece hooded sweatshirt to wear well and with pride.

This sexy underwear is knit from Cool Comfort® fabric that wicks away moisture to keep you cool and dry all day. These stretch cotton/modal boxer briefs are also made with Hanes®'s FreshIQ™ advanced odor protection technology that removes odor for all-day freshness. And here's even more comfort - the Comfort Flex® stretch waistband moves with you and keeps its shape wash after wash without pinching or binding. No-ride-up leg bands are designed to stay smoothly in place and there's a traditional open fly. These moisture-wicking stretch boxer briefs are available in a convenient 4-pack of assorted solid colors for effortless stocking up.

Their iconic Crocs comfort is perfect for all-day wear, and the ventilation ports enhance breathability while quickly shedding water and debris - Material with a Purpose: The Classis Clog is made with our innovative Croslite compound, which now contains 25% bio-circular materials like cooking oil from other industries and is calculated through mass balance (ISCC PLUS Certified)
full_description: Original. Versatile. Comfortable. Classic Clog It’s the iconic clog that started a comfort revolution around the world! The irreverent go-to comfort shoe that you're sure to fall deeper in love with day after day. Crocs Classic Clogs offer lightweight Iconic Crocs Comfort, a color for every personality, and an ongoing invitation to be comfortable in your own shoes. Croslite Styles Classic Clog - New Colors Classic Sandal 2.0 Classic Slide 2.0 Classic Flip 2.0 Iconic Crocs Comfort ✔ Croslite Material Water-Friendly Lightweight Customizable with Jibbitz What is Croslite? Croslite is what our Classic Clogs and most of our shoes are made from. It’s our innovative compound proprietary to Crocs that helps provide the comfort you know and love. Croslite accounts for more than 80% of our total footwear materials use. Does this help the environment? YES! Moving to bio-circular materials helps to reduce carbon dioxide emissions! What is bio-circular material? Bio-circular materials repurpose plant-based byproducts that would have otherwise ended up as waste, like cooking oil from other industries. Bio-circular materials are less emissions-intensive than their virgin, fossil-fuel based counterparts.

name: Hanes Men's Zip-Up Hoodie, EcoSmart Fleece Full-Zip Hoodie for Men, Hooded Sweatshirt
small_description: FLEECE TO FEEL GOOD ABOUT – EcoSmart mid-weight cotton/poly fleece with up to 5% of the poly fibers. - CLASSIC ZIP-FRONT SILHOUETTE – Full-zip front with a drawstring hood and front pockets. - MADE TO STAY SOFT – Pill-resistant durable fleece stays warm and cozy. - HOLDS ITS SHAPE - Thanks to ribbed cuffs and hem. - MADE TO LAST – Double-needle stitching at the neck and armhole seams for quality and durability, plus a dyed-to-match drawstring at the hood. - CONVENIENT TEARAWAY TAGS - Getting rid of itchy tags is super easy. Simply tear it off for comfort that lasts all day.
full_description: Your comfort and your values can go hand-in-hand when you choose a zip-front hooded sweatshirt you can feel good about buying and feel good about wearing. Hanes® EcoSmart® fleece is your new go-to wardrobe staple. Soft and plush, this cozy zip-up fleece hoodie is made of mid-weight cotton/poly fleece with up to 5% of the poly fibers. The fleece in this classic zip-front hooded jacket is super soft and thick, and made to keep its warm, cozy feel. And it will hold its shape thanks to ribbed cuffs and hem. Double-needle stitching at the neck and armhole seams further enhance quality and sturdiness. In classic hoodie style, there's a split kangaroo pocket and a dyed-to-match drawstring at the hood. Here's a soft, warm, fleece zip-up hooded sweatshirt to wear well and with pride.
